Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.86,0:00:41.90,OP,,0,0,0,,追悔昨日的人 都是事後諸葛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.92,0:00:45.48,OP,,0,0,0,,嘗試著把身體交給音樂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.48,0:00:48.57,OP,,0,0,0,,會讓心情變得輕鬆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.57,0:00:51.59,OP,,0,0,0,,現在不就像飛翔一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.59,0:00:55.33,OP,,0,0,0,,「因為那裡有山啊」這樣回答的登山者
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.33,0:00:58.85,OP,,0,0,0,,結果答案很單純
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.85,0:01:02.98,OP,,0,0,0,,就是一個不斷挑戰的旅人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.98,0:01:06.08,OP,,0,0,0,,你看就連雨水 也轉變成能量
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.08,0:01:09.86,OP,,0,0,0,,展開笑顏吧 跳起舞來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.58,0:01:13.80,OP,,0,0,0,,向太陽展示我們的步伐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.80,0:01:18.06,OP,,0,0,0,,繼續前進的話 我們就自由了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.06,0:01:24.28,OP,,0,0,0,,一起升入天空的煙火 就讓心境如一
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.28,0:01:27.50,OP,,0,0,0,,太陽升升落落
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.50,0:01:31.66,OP,,0,0,0,,即使不能保證明天天晴
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.66,0:01:38.75,OP,,0,0,0,,無論波濤多麼洶湧 也能變得應付自如
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.75,0:01:44.06,OP,,0,0,0,,命運的樂園就在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.92,0:22:37.01,ED,,0,0,0,,無論什麼時候 都在想念
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.01,0:22:42.89,ED,,0,0,0,,不能見面的日子 Everytime I Feel
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.89,0:22:46.58,ED,,0,0,0,,啊 掌心裡握住的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.58,0:22:49.59,ED,,0,0,0,,包裹住的 Heart&Soul
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.59,0:22:55.11,ED,,0,0,0,,永不離開的 一直在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.11,0:23:00.72,ED,,0,0,0,,不期的 溫柔的 每次邂逅
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.72,0:23:06.48,ED,,0,0,0,,變得想要全部擁有
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.48,0:23:12.44,ED,,0,0,0,,I Will-Be As One- 想要守護你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.44,0:23:18.54,ED,,0,0,0,,Stay With Me 喜歡你 Yes You 親愛的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.54,0:23:25.21,ED,,0,0,0,,滿溢而出的想念 不必隱藏 因為能夠傳達
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.21,0:23:30.31,ED,,0,0,0,,僅有的一次相遇的奇蹟
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.31,0:23:36.31,ED,,0,0,0,,就如群星一起閃耀那樣 雨滴最終匯入大海
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.31,0:23:45.91,ED,,0,0,0,,兩個人 在一起吧 Love 你就是全部
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.29,0:00:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,妖精的尾巴 到上集為止是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.59,0:00:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,開始移動的涅盤所前往的目的地是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.87,0:00:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,溫迪她們的公會怪貓之家
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.62,0:00:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,是的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.61,0:00:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我們跟毒龍眼鏡蛇對決了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.32,0:00:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,是的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.33,0:00:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 鳩拉大叔像不像馬鈴薯呀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.07,0:00:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我才不是馬鈴薯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.86,0:01:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,總覺得我 渾身沒力氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.37,0:01:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,是那傢伙的毒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.17,0:02:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.95,0:02:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我的身體也…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.63,0:02:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,而且還在交通工具上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.86,0:02:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,賭上六魔的榮耀 也要打倒你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.45,0:02:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,聖十的鳩拉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.37,0:02:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,可…可惡 身體…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.20,0:02:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我聽見了哦 你生命將終結的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.87,0:02:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,消失吧 舊時代的滅龍魔導士
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.64,0:02:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,已經夠了 眼鏡蛇
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.02,0:03:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,布萊恩 你幹什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.62,0:03:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你已經幹的不錯了 好好休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.08,0:03:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,哼 反正也是冒牌的滅龍魔導士
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.20,0:03:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我不需要敗給正規公會的六魔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.28,0:03:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,這個垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.08,0:03:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,聽見了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.54,0:03:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,可惡 可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.90,0:03:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.23,0:03:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是想聽聽那唯一的朋友的聲音而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.19,0:03:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,修貝利烏斯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.72,0:03:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,眼鏡蛇
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.97,0:04:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你們不是同伴嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.86,0:04:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,同伴 這東西以後要多少都會有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.74,0:04:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,用涅盤的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.53,0:04:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,那根本就不能稱為同伴了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.64,0:04:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,那只是牽線木偶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.02,0:04:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,別那麼斤斤計較的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.44,0:04:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我倒是很讚賞你的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.81,0:04:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道我的意思吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.16,0:04:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,就讓你成為第一個牽線木偶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.22,0:04:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我竟然輸…輸了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.59,0:04:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,持有強烈信念的人會勝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.99,0:04:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,鳩拉曾這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.13,0:05:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,不要 我不想輸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.69,0:05:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,如果輸了就會被爸爸拋棄
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.18,0:05:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想輸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.90,0:05:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,逃也沒用
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.44,0:05:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我的天眼可以將一切看清穿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.63,0:05:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,看見了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.01,0:05:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,液化大地
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.01,0:05:27.32,Zhushi,,0,0,0,,liquid ground
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.21,0:05:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣下去會被拋棄的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.45,0:05:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,被爸爸拋棄的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.31,0:05:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,也許那樣反而是好的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.60,0:06:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,六魔將軍在今天終結
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.55,0:06:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.82,0:06:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,納茲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.19,0:06:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,到底怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.18,0:06:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,因為這是交通工具
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.55,0:06:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,大家
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.05,0:06:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,哈比
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.99,0:06:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,小貓殿下也平安無事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.00,0:06:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,小貓殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.95,0:06:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,大家快去救救納茲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.14,0:06:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,他要被帶走了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.66,0:06:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,六魔已經失去了半數成員
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.29,0:06:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,衰敗了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.96,0:06:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,為了組成全新的六魔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.96,0:06:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要這個男人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.56,0:07:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,本來就會想到會有這麼一天
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.58,0:07:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,沒想到還真被暗黑公會挖了牆角啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.15,0:07:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,納茲才不會順你們意的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.68,0:07:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,涅盤會將他的內心變成黑暗的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.87,0:07:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,成為我的左膀右臂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.81,0:07:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,想得美
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.96,0:07:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,還有那麼大的力氣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.29,0:07:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,似乎身體狀況不佳啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.73,0:07:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,那傢伙對於交通工具可是極限的脆弱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.54,0:07:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,快點…把…這傢伙…打倒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.02,0:07:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,把這個…停下來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.50,0:07:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然不是為了你 但我會把它停住的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.53,0:07:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.46,0:07:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,停下？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.11,0:07:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,涅盤？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.52,0:08:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你們能做到嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.23,0:08:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,這座城市馬上就要到達
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.47,0:08:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,第一個目的地
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.01,0:08:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,怪貓之家了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.67,0:08:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,是溫迪和夏露露的公會
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.67,0:08:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.41,0:08:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,說出你的目的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.35,0:08:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼要把溫迪殿下的公會作為目標
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.22,0:08:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,超級反轉魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.79,0:08:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,能在一瞬間將光明公會陷入黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.06,0:08:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,真是令人期待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.96,0:08:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,能看見地獄哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.50,0:08:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,絕不能原諒這個傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.28,0:08:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,真狠啊 這個混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.97,0:08:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有聽見嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.08,0:08:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,說出你的目的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.46,0:09:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,對你這種雜碎我沒什麼好說的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.03,0:09:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我要用光明與黑暗的審判
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.50,0:09:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,讓你們俯首稱臣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.37,0:09:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,真是讓人頭痛的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.23,0:09:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.41,0:09:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,都不能正常的對話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.10,0:09:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.61,0:09:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,蛆蟲們
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.71,0:09:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,什…什麼…這個魔力是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.14,0:09:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,站起來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.18,0:09:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,在你找出把怪貓之家當做目標的理由之前
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.63,0:09:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,是不會讓你睡過去的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.01,0:10:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,難…難道…這個大叔…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.41,0:10:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,超級厲害的說
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.45,0:10:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,這就是與首領一樣擁有聖十稱號的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.74,0:10:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,原來如此啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.45,0:10:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,真是讓人有點吃驚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.53,0:10:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,看來聖十的稱號並非浪得虛名
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.98,0:10:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,比起怪貓之家更近的公會有很多
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.32,0:10:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,特地把那裡當做目標
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.15,0:10:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,肯定有特別的理由啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.87,0:11:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,將死之人根本沒有必要知道這些
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.74,0:11:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,常暗迴旋曲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.74,0:11:07.84,Zhushi,,0,0,0,,dark rondo
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.42,0:11:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,岩鐵壁
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.42,0:11:29.60,Zhushi,,0,0,0,,rockiron wall
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.30,0:11:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,哇…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.36,0:11:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,厲害…太厲害了…讓人有點恐怖…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.54,0:11:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你難道不明白這個只是無謂的鬥爭嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.15,0:11:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,快點說出你瞄準怪貓之家的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.76,0:11:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你問了又有何用
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.58,0:11:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我說過這個是沒用的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.80,0:11:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.30,0:12:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,上鉤了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.65,0:12:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.76,0:12:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,大叔 後面
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.81,0:12:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,常暗奇想曲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.81,0:12:09.45,Zhushi,,0,0,0,,dark capriccio
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.64,0:12:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,岩石扭曲了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.59,0:12:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,沒用的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.68,0:12:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,常暗奇想曲是具有貫穿性的魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.68,0:12:30.52,Zhushi,,0,0,0,,{\pos(287,435)}dark capriccio
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.17,0:12:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,這種岩石能輕易穿透的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.64,0:12:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,那樣的話 岩鐵壁是抵擋不住的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.64,0:12:41.92,Zhushi,,0,0,0,,{\pos(400,435)}rockiron wall
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.30,0:12:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,能讓它貫穿的魔法雖然很厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.76,0:12:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,但能躲過那個魔法的人更厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.28,0:12:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你趕快修正一下自己說過的話吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.52,0:12:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,這個可不是沒用的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.17,0:12:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,接下來 怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.02,0:13:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,聖十的魔導士
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.64,0:13:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,常暗奇想曲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.64,0:13:04.64,Zhushi,,0,0,0,,dark capriccio
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.29,0:13:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,岩鐵壁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.29,0:13:06.88,Zhushi,,0,0,0,,rockiron wall
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.56,0:13:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,哈哈…又做一樣的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.98,0:13:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是說過這個是沒用的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.60,0:13:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,很快常暗奇想曲就要粉碎你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.60,0:13:20.95,Zhushi,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355,435)}dark capriccio
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.45,0:13:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,要是那樣就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.59,0:13:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,這個是最後了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.19,0:13:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,而且是特大的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.31,0:13:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,常暗奇想曲 呼嘯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.31,0:13:35.44,Zhushi,,0,0,0,,dark capriccio scream
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.15,0:13:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,岩鐵壁 連鎖
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.15,0:13:39.73,Zhushi,,0,0,0,,rockiron wall chain
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.98,0:13:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,鳩拉 快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.88,0:14:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,用岩石把他封住了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.05,0:14:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,霸王岩碎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.05,0:14:18.22,Zhushi,,0,0,0,,supreme rock shatter
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.56,0:14:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,能承受住這麼厲害的攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.20,0:14:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,還能察覺到要利用岩石的碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.90,0:14:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,怪不得里恩用敬語稱呼他
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.30,0:14:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,幹掉他了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.75,0:14:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,這傢伙是六魔將軍的老大吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.22,0:14:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我們勝利了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.19,0:14:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,快點說出瞄準溫迪殿下公會的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.93,0:14:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,吶…把這個停下來不就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.16,0:15:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,為了我 也請 一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.86,0:15:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,沒想到我居然會被打敗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.20,0:15:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,暗夜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.96,0:15:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,之後就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.43,0:15:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,六魔將軍絕不能被打倒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.55,0:15:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,在六個願望消失的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.63,0:15:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,那位大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.70,0:15:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,那位大人？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.72,0:15:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我說 這個傢伙的臉上…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.79,0:15:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,好像消失了一條紋線
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.76,0:15:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,不要說那麼恐怖的事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.13,0:15:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,會做噩夢的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.95,0:15:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,大家
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.18,0:15:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,溫迪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.18,0:15:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我就說怎麼這麼吵 果真是你們
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.19,0:15:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,夏露露
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.82,0:16:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,這座都市
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.58,0:16:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,好像正朝著我們的公會移動
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.90,0:16:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,好事是的 但是已經沒問題了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.22,0:16:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.94,0:16:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,耍蛇的在對面也被打敗了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.34,0:16:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.87,0:16:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,可能操縱著涅盤的就是這個布萊恩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.91,0:16:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,將他打倒了 也就能停止這個都市的移動了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.27,0:16:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,真叫人不爽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.23,0:16:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,最終還是不知道為什麼瞄準怪貓之家的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.65,0:16:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,算了 可能也沒有什麼深意吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.01,0:16:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,六個願望消失的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.05,0:16:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,那位大人就…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.91,0:16:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然還是有些叫人在意的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.66,0:16:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,不過事情算是結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.72,0:16:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,還…還沒有結束
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.15,0:17:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,快點把這個停下來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.38,0:17:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,納茲 難道是中毒了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.46,0:17:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,公貓也是 真是沒出息啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.44,0:17:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,啊咿
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.91,0:17:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.98,0:17:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.33,0:17:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,做了一個夢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.02,0:17:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你也做了一個夢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.60,0:17:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,在這深夜裡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.90,0:17:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,魔法是打不中我的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.49,0:18:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,暗夜的傷痕不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.51,0:18:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我是超越了我父親的最強的魔導士
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.38,0:18:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.22,0:18:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,弟弟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.60,0:18:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,真希望能再一次 看到你的面容
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.82,0:18:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,第五個願望消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.09,0:18:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,暗夜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.65,0:18:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你絕對不能消失啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.29,0:18:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,那就是我的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.52,0:19:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,到底是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.41,0:19:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.31,0:19:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.47,0:19:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,就沒有像是能控制都市的東西嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.18,0:19:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,怎樣做才能讓它停下來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.56,0:19:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.25,0:19:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,本以為打到了布萊恩就能讓它停下來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.58,0:19:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我們太天真了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.95,0:19:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,居然不知道停止的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.74,0:19:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.19,0:19:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,明明都施了解毒的魔法了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.23,0:19:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,納茲還是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.00,0:19:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,納茲是怕做交通工具啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.80,0:19:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,真是丟臉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.78,0:19:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,啊… 好噁心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.15,0:19:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,暈交通工具？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.73,0:19:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,啊咿
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.55,0:19:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,那樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.83,0:20:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,也許調養平衡感的魔法會有效
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.49,0:20:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,特洛伊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.49,0:20:04.09,Zhushi,,0,0,0,,troia
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.99,0:20:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,哇哦 復活了 沒事了 沒事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.97,0:20:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了 能起作用
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.36,0:20:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,真厲害啊 溫迪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.41,0:20:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,教我這個魔法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.90,0:20:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,因為是天空魔法 你學不來的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.17,0:20:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,這個 沒有乘交通工具的真實感
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.23,0:20:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,好 露西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.94,0:20:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,請你叫船或者列車的星靈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.73,0:20:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有那種東西啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.76,0:20:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,話說 現在不是說這個的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.37,0:20:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你給我看清楚狀況
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.35,0:20:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我們不知道停止的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.91,0:20:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,就像你看到的這個房間裡什麼都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.67,0:20:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,可是操縱著城市的就是這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.83,0:20:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,禾特…理察德是這樣說的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.42,0:20:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我覺得理察德殿下是不會說謊的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.95,0:21:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,在說停止不停止之前
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.54,0:21:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你們誰都沒注意到還有更加不自然的事情嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.06,0:21:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有操控席 王之室裡空無一人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.83,0:21:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,布萊恩也被打倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.08,0:21:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,可是為什麼這東西還在動
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.64,0:21:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,莫非是 自動操控
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.66,0:21:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,已經連涅盤的發生操作也設定好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.79,0:21:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我們的…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.65,0:21:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,公會…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.34,0:21:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,不要緊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.15,0:21:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,公會不會有事的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.92,0:21:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,讓我還你這個人情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.85,0:21:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我一定會讓它停下來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.77,0:22:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,涅盤是不會停下來的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.67,0:22:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,只要我還健在
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.05,0:24:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,納茲的話裡面 沒有什麼內涵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.13,0:24:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有沒有 我也說了很多有用的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.68,0:24:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,例如說
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.79,0:24:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,那個 你看 像「燃燒吧」「去幹掉他」之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.66,0:24:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,那只是單純的口頭禪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.34,0:24:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,下回 正因為是你的話語
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.01,0:24:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,不是這樣的啦 是能夠讓人留在心上的話喲
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.44,0:24:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我要揍你囉
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.53,0:24:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,不過也沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.60,0:24:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,這個留下來的只是心理陰影
